item.content:encoded:
Homesick offers specialized candles that tap into your sensory memory through nostalgic scents.

Fill your space with fragrances reminding you of the people, places, and moments that matter most. Whether it be a road trip to college in Texas or baking cookies with grandma in Maine, home is always where the heart is.
About this item
  • Top Notes: Orange, Bay Leaf, Beignet; Mid Notes: Allspice, Gardenia, Rose, Base Notes: Sugar, Vanilla, Musk
  • Gardenia flowers line the historic Garden District King cakes topped with cinnamon and warm beignets celebrate Mardi Gras traditions
  • 13.75 oz
  • 60-80 hour burn time
  • All natural soy wax blend
  • Hand poured in the USA
  • Candle Care: Keep wick trimmed to ¼ inch, Burn for 2-3 hours at a time, Extinguish flame completely when done
Bring home to you, no matter where you are
